      <title>NexT 7.6.0 Released</title>
      <link href="/2019/12/01/next-7-6-0-released/"/>
      <url>/2019/12/01/next-7-6-0-released/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="üí•-Breaking-Changes"><a href="#üí•-Breaking-Changes" class="headerlink" title="üí• Breaking Changes"></a>üí• Breaking Changes</h2><h3 id="Remove-rss-button-1291"><a href="#Remove-rss-button-1291" class="headerlink" title="Remove rss button (#1291)"></a>Remove rss button (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI5MQ==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1291">#1291<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</h3><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-# hexo-generator-feed required for rss support. Leave rss as blank to use site's feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-# Set rss to false to disable feed link. Set rss to specific value if you have burned your feed already.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-rss:</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"># Social Links</span><br><span class="line"># Usage: `Key: permalink || icon`</span><br><span class="line"># Key is the link label showing to end users.</span><br><span class="line"># Value before `||` delimiter is the target permalink, value after `||` delimiter is the name of Font Awesome icon.</span><br><span class="line">social:</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-  #VK Group: https://vk.com/yourname || vk</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+  #RSS: /atom.xml || rss</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Remove-cheers-and-auto-excerpt-1284"><a href="#Remove-cheers-and-auto-excerpt-1284" class="headerlink" title="Remove cheers and auto_excerpt (#1284)"></a>Remove cheers and auto_excerpt (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI4NA==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1284">#1284<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</h3><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- # Automatically excerpt (Not recommend).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- # Use &lt;!-- more --&gt; in the post to control excerpt accurately.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- auto_excerpt:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   enable: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-   length: 150</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- # Enable \"cheers\" for archive page.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- cheers: true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Drop-NodeJs-8-support-amp-Require-NodeJs-gt-10-1269"><a href="#Drop-NodeJs-8-support-amp-Require-NodeJs-gt-10-1269" class="headerlink" title="Drop NodeJs 8 support &amp; Require NodeJs &gt;= 10 (#1269)"></a>Drop NodeJs 8 support &amp; Require NodeJs &gt;= 10 (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI2OQ==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1269">#1269<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</h3><h3 id="Refactor-front-matter-make-it-has-the-same-key-as-the-configuration-file-1211"><a href="#Refactor-front-matter-make-it-has-the-same-key-as-the-configuration-file-1211" class="headerlink" title="Refactor front-matter: make it has the same key as the configuration file (#1211)"></a>Refactor front-matter: make it has the same key as the configuration file (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTIxMQ==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1211">#1211<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</h3><p>In <strong>post front-matter</strong>:</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">toc:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  number: false</span><br><span class="line">  max_depth: 3</span><br><span class="line">reward_settings:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  comment: Donate comment here.</span><br><span class="line">quicklink:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  delay: true</span><br><span class="line">  timeout: 3000</span><br><span class="line">  priority: true</span><br><span class="line">  ignores:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Some deprecated</span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- toc_max_depth: 4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- toc_number: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- reward: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">- quicklink: true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>In theme‚Äôs <strong>_config.yml</strong>:</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">quicklink:</span><br><span class="line">  # Home page and archive page can be controlled through home and archive options below.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-  home: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-  archive: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+  # This configuration item is independent of `enable`.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+  home: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+  archive: false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="‚≠ê-Features"><a href="#‚≠ê-Features" class="headerlink" title="‚≠ê Features"></a>‚≠ê Features</h2><ul><li>Set inject default extname from file‚Äôs extname (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI4MQ==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1281">#1281<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li><li>Adjust copy-button style (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI3Nw==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1277">#1277<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li><li>Remove include-raw tag (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI2OA==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1268">#1268<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li></ul><h2 id="üêû-Bug-Fixes"><a href="#üêû-Bug-Fixes" class="headerlink" title="üêû Bug Fixes"></a>üêû Bug Fixes</h2><ul><li>Allow decoding post link (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI0Nw==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1247">#1247<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li></ul><h2 id="üõ†-Improvements"><a href="#üõ†-Improvements" class="headerlink" title="üõ† Improvements"></a>üõ† Improvements</h2><ul><li>Make author image optional (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI2Mw==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1263">#1263<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li><li>Update CDN URLs (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTI1Mg==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1252">#1252<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li></ul><h2 id="üåç-Localization"><a href="#üåç-Localization" class="headerlink" title="üåç Localization"></a>üåç Localization</h2><ul><li>New Crowdin translations (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTA3Mw==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1073">#1073<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li><li>New Crowdin translations (<span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3B1bGwvMTE1MQ==" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/pull/1151">#1151<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span>)</li></ul><hr><p>For full changes, see the <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L2NvbXBhcmUvdjcuNS4wLi4udjcuNi4w" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/compare/v7.5.0...v7.6.0">comparison between v7.5.0 and v7.6.0<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></p><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3RoZW1lLW5leHQvaGV4by10aGVtZS1uZXh0L3JlbGVhc2VzL3RhZy92Ny42LjA=" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/releases/tag/v7.6.0">Detailed changes for NexT v7.6.0<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
